column5: Headed up to Morson area in a week or so. Any reports?

t8km What part of the lake do you usually like to fish. Walleyes seem to run a little bigger if you go northwest and they are in like 18 to 28 feet. Crappies were going in the Obabikon but not at Miles but the water was turning over so it was green.
Usually go northwest unless the winds up. Are you fishing points then? How about numbers? Fishing still hot as it was this summer?
